title: I AM ATHLETE | DeSean Jackson On Former Eagles QB Donovan McNabb, Sean Mcvay & Nipsey Hussle

I AM ATHLETE | Episode 35
3X Pro Bowl wide receiver and free agent, DeSean Jackson joins Brandon Marshall, LeSean McCoy and Pacman Jones in episode 35 of I Am Athlete. Watch as the former Philadelphia Eagles receiver discuss his relationship with former Philadelphia QB, Donavan McNabb, L.A. rapper Nipsey Hussle and his future in the NFL.
